Running gem without doing the following will cause a seg fault.

HOW TO PREVENT
log in as root on your machine

type

export CFLAGS="-O2 -fno-tree-dce -fno-optimize-sibling-calls"

type

<enter>

in the root directory of the repository

type 

./installer

type
<enter>

Everything should compile and you should be able to install gems. 
